ACT:
 Pay Scales and revised pay scales of computers shown as identical in the Second Pay Commission Report--Right to be equated as Research Assistants Grade 11 both in status and in pay is entirely within the sphere of the function of the Pay Commission--Effect of the Report of the Third Pay Com- mission.
 Constitution of India, 1950--Article 32 can be resorted to only for the enforcement of Fundamental Rights--Equation of posts is not a duty which the court under Art. 32 or the High Court under Art. 226 was competent to carry out.
 
